<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>٧٣ -<span style="color:#006d98"> وَمِنْهَا قَوْلُهُمْ:</span> <span style="color:#950000">" أَعْرُوا النِّسَاءَ، يَلْزَمْنَ الْحِجَالَ "</span>.<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>٧٤ -<span style="color:#006d98"> وَمِنْهَا قَوْلُهُمْ:</span> <span style="color:#950000">" اتَّقُوا فِراسَةَ الْمُؤْمِنِ فَإِنَّهُ يَنْظُرُ بِنُورِ اللَّهِ تَعَالَى "</span>.<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>